snippet.title: EA SPORTS FC 25 Official Launch Trailer | For The Club
snippet.description:
EA SPORTS FC™ 25 gives you more ways to win for the club. Play #FC25 now with Early Access: http://x.ea.com/82072

Team up with friends in your favourite modes with the new 5v5 Rush, and manage your club to victory as FC IQ delivers more tactical control than ever before. Learn more about FC 25 http://x.ea.com/82097

EA SPORTS FC™Mobile gives you more ways to win for the club anywhere, new season update launches 24th September. Play Now - https://fcmobile.sng.link/Dn1ol/pd11

Subscribe to see more from EA SPORTS FC™: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

#FC25 #FCMobile
